data.description:
Welcome home to Cumberland subdivision! This beautiful 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home is located in the Bellevue area. This newly renovated home features 2 stories of spacious living area. The open concept  living room features a oversize window that brings in natural light beautifully. Large kitchen with granite counter tops stainless steel appliances. Off the kitchen you will find the cutest little powder room.
On the main level the massive master bedroom features a large walk in closet and large bathroom.
As you make your way upstairs you will find three spacious bedrooms on the second floor. Large double car garage and water proofed basement  Owner will consider a lease purchase option.
Call your favorite REALTOR today to schedule your tour.
